comments: Edwards' (MIN) forearm makes contact with Fox's (SAC) head as he is passing the ball.
Gobert (MIN) and Sabonis (SAC) briefly engage and disengage during the pick.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact with Gobert's (MIN) arm prior to making any contact with the ball.
Monk (SAC) is already in McDaniels' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Rivers (MIN) is moving alongside Fox's (SAC) path and he legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) turns to roll and his hand brushes Murray's (SAC) front as he releases away from the pick.
Anderson (MIN) is retreating alongside Monk's (SAC) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) and Fox (SAC) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Sabonis (SAC) places his hand momentarily on Gobert's (MIN) side and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) extends his hands into Gobert (MIN) and dislodges him from his rebounding position.
After Fox (SAC) loses his balance on his own, Edwards (MIN) steps forward towards Fox and marginal contact occurs as Fox recovers the loose ball.
Edwards (MIN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fox (SAC).
Anderson (MIN) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Fox's (SAC) arm prior to the start of Fox's upward shooting motion.
Anderson (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Fox (SAC) during rebounding.
McDaniels (MIN) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and legally lifts his right foot.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Rivers (MIN) brings his forearm towards Murray's (SAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Murray's momentum carries him away from the basket.
Monk's (SAC) hand makes contact with the ball as he defends Gobert (MIN) in the lane.
Lyles (SAC) is already in Edwards' (MIN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Russell (MIN) swipes his arm forward and makes contact with Lyles' (SAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact with the ball and with the part of Gobert's (MIN) hand that is on the ball as he pursues the rebound.
Monk (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball as he deflects Edwards' (MIN) pass.
Monk (SAC) establishes himself in Edwards' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

Edwards (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position on Fox's (SAC) drive with a legal arm to his side. Edwards withdraws his arm before Fox gathers, and then avoids making contact on the shot. The contact after Fox's release and follow through is marginal.
Anderson (MIN) re-establishes himself in the frontcourt before making contact with the ball.
Anderson (MIN) is already in Fox's (SAC) path and he absorbs the contact.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) makes contact with McDaniels' (MIN) head as he defends the shot near the rim.
Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in Fox's (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Fox (SAC) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Russell's (MIN) arm.
The game is stopped due to a clock malfunction.  After correcting the clock play resumes with Sacramento retaining possession.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Lyles (SAC) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
